import React from 'react'
import { BrowserRouter, Route, Routes } from 'react-router-dom'
import NavBar from './Components/NavBar'

export default function App() {
  return (
    <>
    <BrowserRouter>
    <NavBar/>
    <Routes>
<Route path='/' element={Ho}/>
    </Routes>
    </BrowserRouter>
    
      
    </>
  )
}
